add_help(['Get your clothes here.','Everything to keep you looking your best is here.'])
add_help(['Get all your tools here.','Everything a settler needs is available at great prices.'])

add_help(['Thankyou for joining our remote settlement.','Our first task is to build some shelter, but while we are doing that we still need food.','You can help us out by raising pigs for slaughter.','If you want to buy a piglet to raise, let me know by saying you would like to buy one.','Pigs love to eat acorns from under the oak trees that are abundant in this area.'],['I would like to buy a pig', 'Pehaps I will buy one later'])
Pigs love eating apples, when they can find them
You can build a house here once you have earned a claim to some land
Once you have earned your claim you can use it to make out some land by placing it on the ground
The forest is full of wolves and skeletons that are dangerous to your pigs. Be careful
You can herd pigs in the forest where the oak trees grow
Ships from the nearest city come into the jetty occassionally
When you have contributed to our settlement, you will be rewarded with some land
The mausoleum was here when we discovered these lands, and seems to be hundreds of years old. No one knows who built it
Oak trees drop acorns which pigs love to eat. You can also gather strong wood from oak trees suitable for building
You can buy pigs from the sty, and sell them to the butcher once you have helped them grow big enough
This settlement is in the frontier of our lands. We need lots of help to get established
It is said that the undead haunt the area round the ancient mausoleum nearby
The pig sty is where the merchant keeps the young pigs he has for sale
Wolves live in the forest, and will eat pigs if they can catch them. However they prefer ham if they can get it

add_help(['On behalf of the Duke I would like to welcome you to moraf.','If you are new here I suggest talking to the pig seller.','He will tell you what you can do to help out.','If you have decide you would like to settle here I can assign you some land','but you will need to show that you are a useful citizen.','If you can raise 50 coins herding pigs, then a plot of land is yours.'],['I would like to buy a deed','I will come back when I have raised some pigs'])
